city-guide Web site market? The three national services _
Citysearch, Microsoft's Sidewalk and AOL's Digital Cities _ now
find themselve competing with Yahoo, as well as a number of sites
run by big metropolitan newspapers. By Laurie J. Flynn.
</P>
