   COMMENTARY (``k'' category)
</P>
<P>
   MEANS-COLUMN (Washington) _ The polls indicate women are still
backing President Clinton more strongly than men, despite the Starr
report; but the one woman he needs most, First Lady Hillary
Clinton, is distinctly cool to him. Monica Lewinsky says the
president suggested that he and Hillary might divorce following
their White House years. Did he mean it? By MARIANNE MEANS.
</P>
