will not let me type in the name of my server. My Internet provider
tells me it's a Win98 problem and I will have to talk to Microsoft.
Well, I can't find an 800-number for them, and I got so mad that I
damaged my disk. So, what can you do for me, Doc? By DR. EMILIO
BOMBAY. Story will move in ``l'' lifestyle category. &QL; 
