The first question: What are the Seminoles going to do at
quarterback, where Chris Weinke threw a school-record six
interceptions against N.C. State. (Kelly, Paklm Beach Post) ETA 8
p.m. ET.
</P>
<P>
   BOX-BEAN _ Profile on Vaughn Bean, Evander Ho
</P>
</TEXT>
</BODY>
