HOYE-COLUMN (Undated) - You want the next ``killer app''?
</P>
<P>
   I got the next killer app . . . right here.
</P>
<P>
   It's an idea that's bumped around in my head for a few years.
But I think it's time has come. OK. So here's my idea: It's called
the home server. You sell people a powerful PC. They plunk it down
in the den. Then, they use it to run an assortment of computer
appliances spread all over the house. My idea is, simply, to give
people computers that fit into their lives.
