 &QL; 
 &QL; 
TX-MINORITY-ENROLLMENT (undated) _ A story has moved on increased
minority enrollment at University of Texas despite a ban on
affirmative action. By LYDIA LUM.  &QL;
</P>
<P>
   Houston Chronicle  &QL; 
 &QL;
</P>
</TEXT>
