<HEADLINE>
MONDAY NIGHT GAMES LOSE HOUR, TAVERN ATTENDANCE, L.A. BAR OWNERS
SAY
</HEADLINE>
 (For use by NYTimes News Service clients) 
(Will also move in the ``f'' financial news file.) 
